3	 *
4	 * This route handles CRUD operations for gaming cabinets (machines).
5	 * It supports:
6	 * - Fetching cabinets by ID or location
7	 * - Creating new cabinets with deduplication checks
8	 * - Updating existing cabinets (legacy PUT)
9	 * - Soft deleting cabinets (legacy DELETE)
10	 * - Availability checks (serial, SMIB, custom name)
11	 * - Location-based access control
12	 *
